SELECT teamfran.franchName AS name, MAX(100.0 * team.W / team.G) AS winPercentage, SUM(sal.salary) AS payroll, team.W, team.G, teamfran.franchID, team.yearID
FROM Teams AS team, Salaries AS sal 
INNER JOIN teamsFranchises AS teamfran ON
      team.yearID = sal.yearID 
      AND teamfran.franchID = team.franchID 
      AND team.teamID = sal.teamID
      AND team.franchID = teamFran.franchID
      AND team.yearID = sal.yearID
GROUP BY team.franchID, sal.yearID, sal.teamID
